'''克萊兒·德尼'''（{{lang-fr|Claire Denis}}；{{bd|1946年|4月21日}}）是[[法國|法國]]電影導演與編劇。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lesgensducinema.com/affiche_acteur.php?mots=Claire+Denis&nom_acteur=DENIS%20Claire&ident=10587&debut=0&record=0&from=ok|title=Claire Denis|date=9 July 2013|website=Les Gens du Cinéma|accessdate=19 February 2014|language=fr|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021215110/http://www.lesgensducinema.com/affiche_acteur.php?mots=Claire+Denis&nom_acteur=DENIS%20Claire&ident=10587&debut=0&record=0&from=ok|dead-url=no}} This site uses Denis' birth certificate as its source of information.</ref>

== 生平 ==
克萊兒·德尼出生於法國巴黎，但她在法屬非洲成長，跟隨擔任公務員的父親，他們一家住過[[布吉納法索|布吉納法索]]、[[喀麥隆|喀麥隆]]、[[法屬索馬里蘭|法屬索馬里蘭]]與[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]]<ref>Hermione Eyre, "Claire Denis on filmmaking and feminism," ''Prospect'', 21 June 2010, [http://www.prospectmagazine.co.uk/2010/06/loving-the-lost-and-monstrous/] {{Wayback|url=http://www.prospectmagazine.co.uk/2010/06/loving-the-lost-and-monstrous/ |date=20110703174440 }}</ref>；她在14歲時與母親、妹妹搬回法國定居。<ref>Beugnet (2004). ''Claire Denis'', p. 14.</ref>由於童年的西非經驗，她後來在許多作品中處理非洲的殖民與後殖民議題。

1988年，她完成首部長片《{{link-fr|巧克力 (1988年電影)|Chocolat (film, 1988)|巧克力}}》，片中半自傳地觸碰到非洲殖民議題，進入[[坎城影展|第41屆坎城影展]]正式競賽單元；另外她也以《{{link-fr|無恐無懼|S'en fout la mort}}》(1990)、《{{link-fr|心之潛蝕|L'Intrus (film, 2004)}}》(2004)與《{{link-fr|白鬼子|White Material}}》(2009)三度獲選為[[威尼斯影展|威尼斯影展]]正式競賽片。2022年，她以《{{link-de|帶著愛與決心|Avec amour et acharnement}}》獲選為[[第72屆柏林影展|第72屆柏林影展]]正式競賽片<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2022/film/global/berlin-film-festival-competition-encounter-titles-1235157036/ |title=Berlin Selection Unveiled: Claire Denis, Hong Sangsoo, Rithy Panh, Dario Argento Head to Festival |first=Naman |last=Ramachandran |date=2022-01-19 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |access-date=2022-01-20 |archive-date=2022-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220214201156/https://variety.com/2022/film/global/berlin-film-festival-competition-encounter-titles-1235157036/ }}</ref>，並獲得[[最佳導演銀熊獎|最佳導演銀熊獎]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2022/film/festivals/berlin-film-festival-award-winners-live-1235183888/|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=16 February 2022|title=Spanish Drama ‘Alcarràs’ Wins Golden Bear at Berlin Film Festival|first1=Guy|last1=Lodge|first2=Leo|last2=Barraclough|access-date=17 February 2022|archive-date=2022-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220531021354/https://variety.com/2022/film/festivals/berlin-film-festival-award-winners-live-1235183888/}}</ref>。

